Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: President Alfonsin of Argentina
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xbxt
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Dec 1983
US hopes of new talks follow installation of Argentina's first democratically-elected president, Alfonsin. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less